<para>
增加<type>timestamp</type>的数据范围 (John Cochran)
</para>
</listitem>

   <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
     Change <literal>EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM timestamp)</literal> so
     <type>timestamp without time zone</type> is assumed to be in
