更改<literal>EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM timestamp)</literal>，
这样<type>timestamp without time zone</type>假设为本地时间，而不是GMT (Tom)
</para>
   </listitem>

   <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>Trap division by zero in case the operating system doesn't prevent it (Tom)</para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
在操作系统不阻止除以零的情况下阻止被零除 (Tom)
</para>
</listitem>
   <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>Change the <type>numeric</type> data type internally to base 10000 (Tom)</para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
改变<type>numeric</type>数据类型内部基于10000 (Tom)
</para>
</listitem>
   <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>New <function>hostmask()</function> function (Greg Wickham)</para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
